dcterms:description: The UIEB dataset consists of 950 underwater images, which are split into a training set of 800 samples, a validation set of 90 samples, and a challenge set of 60 samples. Each sample includes a raw degraded underwater image and its corresponding human-curated reference image.
dcterms:title: UIEB

dcterms:description: The UCCS dataset includes three different underwater color settings: bluish, greenish, and blue-green tones, with each setting containing 100 images, totaling 300 images.
dcterms:title: UCCS
